---
---
<section class="relative min-h-[795px] flex items-center bg-[#0B0C10] overflow-hidden">
  

  <!-- Decorative background element -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full bg-[#004E98]/5 blur-[120px] -z-0"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center py-20 relative z-10">
    <div class="z-10">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 mb-6">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-pulse"></span>
        <span class="font-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/70">✓ Atendimento 100% Online para todo o Brasil</span>
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold leading-[1.05] tracking-tighter mb-8 text-white">
        Móveis Planejados de <span class="text-[#FBB03B]">Alto Padrão</span> com Preço Direto de Fábrica.
      </h1>
      
      <div class="font-body text-lg text-white/80 max-w-xl mb-10 leading-relaxed">
        <p class="mb-6">Sou Willian Scariott, projetista e montador há mais de 6 anos. Eu crio a engenharia técnica para você comprar móveis direto da fábrica, garantindo:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#FBB03B] font-bold">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Otimização de chapa</strong> via Corte Cloud.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#FBB03B] font-bold">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Zero lucros embutidos</strong> de lojas e marcenarias.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#FBB03B] font-bold">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Execução e montagem</strong> sem erros.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <a href="https://wa.me/5551996532525?text=Ol%C3%A1%20Willian%21%20Quero%20garantir%20um%20projeto%20100%25%20execut%C3%A1vel%20no%20Cortecloud%2C%20com%20plano%20de%20corte%20otimizado%20e%20zero%20margem%20de%20erro." class="bg-[#FBB03B] text-black px-8 py-4 font-label font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5">
          Falar sobre o Meu Projeto
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="chat">chat</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/#como-funciona" class="border border-white/20 text-white/70 px-8 py-4 font-label font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white/5 transition-all duration-300 rounded-md shadow-md hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5">
          Como funciona a economia
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative">
      <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-surface-container-high relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl rounded-sm">
        <img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-100 contrast-110" data-alt="Willian Scariott - Especialista em Marcenaria Digital" src="/Hero.webp"/>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0B0C10] via-transparent to-transparent opacity-60"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
